{"about_the_game":"You are sent to a remote island where a deadly virus has turned the population into zombies. Your mission: destroy infected nests with molotovs, collect samples, and survive long enough to signal for rescue. To succeed, you\u2019ll need to master a variety of survival mechanics, including:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Base Building &amp; Fortifications<br />\r\nConstruct a customizable base using salvaged materials to protect yourself from nightly zombie hordes.<br />\r\nUpgrade walls, doors, and defensive structures like traps, spikes, and turrets.<br />\r\nBuild resource stations like crafting benches, storage units, and workstations for advanced upgrades.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Crafting System<br />\r\nCollect resources like wood, metal, to craft weapons, molotovs, medical supplies, and tools.<br />\r\nCreate advanced gear such as reinforced armor, or explosive traps.<br />\r\nUnlock rare blueprints for high-tech items through exploration.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Zombie Hordes<br />\r\nSurvive waves of increasingly dangerous zombie hordes that adapt to your tactics.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Resource Management<br />\r\nManage your stamina, hunger, and health while scavenging for supplies.<br />\r\nBalance time between foraging for food, gathering building materials, and defending your base.<br />\r\nKeep your gear in top condition\u2014tools and weapons degrade over time and must be repaired.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Advanced Combat<br />\r\nUse a mix of melee weapons, ranged firearms, and throwable explosives to fight off zombies.<br />\r\nStealth mechanics let you avoid large groups of enemies or set up ambushes.<br />\r\nCombat upgrades unlock special abilities like stronger attacks or faster crafting under pressure.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Mission Objectives<br />\r\nBurn zombie nests to retrieve infection samples, but beware of the hordes they attract.<br />\r\nConstruct a beacon to signal for extraction, but defending it against the final zom